snippet.title: BLACKFROST -- The Long Dark 2 -- Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist BLACKFROST: The Long Dark 2, on Steam.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1586260?utm_source=youtube-com&utm_medium=tga-trailer&utm_campaign=tga-wishlist&utm_content=cta

For more information:

https://www.hinterland.com/creations/blackfrost

The music in the trailer is "Parliament of Owls", by Agnes Obel. Hinterland has secured permission to use this music for the trailer.
